These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, engineer
1. the bartender is in an even position##4
2. the engineer is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku |
| Job     | engineer    | bartender   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, handball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | fanta | iced-tea        |
| Sport      | rugby  | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, american
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | d&b |
| Nationality   | indonesian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: plum, asparagus
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | almond-milk |
| Food       | plum | asparagus    |

 #################################

 
